Class ProfileDaoHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hoovler.dao.resources.ProfileDaoHelper

  • public class ProfileDaoHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton object that assists in the creation of the Profile object, and is reponsible for auto-populating the DefaultProfileDao repository.

      • getProfilesMap

        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,Profile> getProfilesMap(java.lang.String sourceUrl)
        Parses the source JSON for the profiles list, and build the Profile object, included the nested Headshot and Social[] objects.

        For the profiles list specifically, this method is preferable to the standard parsing methods within most common JSON packages because there none of those parsing utilities offer the option to create empty object members when, given an array of JSON objects, some objects do not have those members.

        Parameters:
        sourceUrl - the URL of the source JSON profiles list.
        Returns:
        a HashMap<String, Profile> map wherein the Profile.getId() is the key, and the Profile object is the value.
